<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>ProMut</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  {% include "head.html.jinja2" %}

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/index' + infix + '.css') }}" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container-navbar">
    <div class="row pt-4 align-items-center">
      <div class="col-sm-3 col-8 offset-2 offset-sm-0">
        <img class="logo-promut" alt="ProMut" src="{{ url_for('static', filename='img/logo.png') }}" />
      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-9 col-12 text-sm-right mt-4 mt-sm-0">
        {% if not current_user.is_authenticated %}
        <div class="btn-group">
          <a href="/auth/provisional-login" class="btn btn-primary d-block d-sm-inline">
            Provisional login
          </a>
          <a href="{{ url_for('google.login') }} " class="btn btn-primary d-block d-sm-inline">
            <i class="fab fa-google mr-2"></i>
            Log in
          </a>

          <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary dropdown-toggle dropdown-toggle-split" data-toggle="dropdown"
            aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="sr-only">Toggle Dropdown</span>
          </button>

          <div class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right">
            <a class="dropdown-item" href="{{ url_for('auth.demo_log_in') }}">Demo mode</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="skew-bar my-4"></div>

  <div class="container-main">
    <div class="row mt-5">
      <div class="landing-title-container">
        <p class="landing-title">
          A platform for machine translation literacy acquisition
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5 landing-row-container">
      <div class="col-sm-4 col-12 subtitle">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary subtitle">Welcome to ProMut</h2>
        <p>
          The ProMut platform extends and improves the former MutNMT platform to incorporate new features for advance
          machine translation literacy acquisition. The full workflow, from data to training, testing, inspection and
          evaluation has been completely reviewed in ProMut. Code is open-source, enabling deployment of instances in a
          distributed way.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4 col-12 mt-3 mt-sm-0">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary subtitle">LT-LiDER project</h2>
        <p>
          LT-LiDER is a project that aims at mapping the landscape of technological capabilities required to work as
          language or translation expert. It also aims at generating the necessary outputs to improve trainersâ€™s skills
          and motivate them to adopt appropriate pedagogical approaches and strategies for integrating technology into
          their language or translation classrooms.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4 col-12 mt-3 mt-sm-0">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary subtitle">The Former MutNMT</h2>
        <p>
          You are invited to check out MutNMT, an online platform to learn Neural Machine Translation by doing. This web
          application lets the user train, inspect, evaluate and translate using neural engines.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row my-5 align-items-center footer">
      <div class="col-12 col-sm-2">
        <h2 class="h5 text-primary dramatic-subtitle">Find us on</h2>
        <a href="https://github.com/Prompsit/ProMut" class="h1 text-dark">
          <i class="fab fa-github-square"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-sm-2">
        <h2 class="h5 text-primary dramatic-subtitle">Powered by</h2>
        <a href="https://marian-nmt.github.io/" class="h1 text-dark">
          <img alt="MARIANNMT" src="{{ url_for('static', filename='img/marian-logo.png') }}" style="width: 140px;" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-sm-8 text-sm-right mt-4 mt-sm-0">
        <img alt="" src="{{ url_for('static', filename='img/lt-lider-logo.jpg') }}" style="width: 200px;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='lib/jquery-3.5.1.min.js') }}"></script>
  <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='lib/bootstrap.bundle.min.js') }}"></script>
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/driver.js/dist/driver.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>